title: Deebo Samuel to Jets? Mock Draft continues, Cardinals on Kyler Murray,  Bills SB or bust, and Who goes #1?
itunes:title: Deebo Samuel to Jets? Mock Draft continues, Cardinals on Kyler Murray,  Bills SB or bust, and Who goes #1?
description:
The Good Morning Football Podcast begins with the Jets possibly being interested in WR Deebo Samuel.  Hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Super Bowl Champion Shaun O'Hara discuss if Samuel is worth NY putting together an offer. The table continues its Mock Draft with picks 9-16 before applauding the Cardinals for closing the door on any discussions around trading QB Kyler Murray.  Is it Super Bowl or bust for the Bills this season?  We wrap up the week with Jimmy G's best case scenario and who we think is taken #1 overall in the NFL Draft.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
